  <p class="eyebrow">The basics</p>
  <h2 class="sec">The basics.</h2>

  <h3>What is Uncost, in one sentence?</h3>
  <p>A nonprofit, nonpartisan movement to reduce the cost of living by directing AI, robotics, open-source tools, and shared infrastructure toward the essentials — starting with evidence, not promises.</p>

  <h3>Is this a political party or campaign?</h3>
  <p>No. Uncost is strictly nonpartisan. We publish open data and public-interest analysis and welcome people across the political spectrum. We don&rsquo;t back candidates, run campaigns, or do partisan lobbying.</p>

  <h3>Is this crypto, a token, or a DAO?</h3>
  <p>No — deliberately. There are no tokens, no on-chain voting, and no crypto mechanics. The Assembly&rsquo;s value is trust and participation, not financial speculation.</p>

  <h3>Are you against work?</h3>
  {{ gap("faq-q-against-work", "the forced-work / basic-needs-behind-a-paycheck framing is design-authored and not in the July MOVEMENT_PLAN or CONTROL; author from the vision before it ships") }}
